transitdroid.domain.entities.user

Class User

  • java.lang.Object
    • transitdroid.domain.core.DomainObject
      • transitdroid.domain.entities.user.User
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IDomainObject, IUser

    public class User
extends DomainObject
implements IUser
    User Class contains private attributes indicating specific information about the User. The firstName, lastName,userName, a byte[] password, ICard, the byte[] salt, and a list of UserRole.
    Author:
    TransitDroid Team
